w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bruce-springsteen-patti-smith@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bruce-springsteen-patti-smith@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bruce-springsteen-patti-smith@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bruce-springsteen-patti-smith@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bruce-springsteen-patti-smith@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀（Bruce Springsteen）</a>参加了全明星阵容，本周即将举行的纽约帕蒂<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/patti-smith">·史密斯（Patti Smith）</a>致敬音乐会。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/bruce-springsteen-live-in-london-setlist-photos-3466084"><b>布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀（Bruce Springsteen）住在伦敦：Heartland Hero仍然坚定地处于雄伟的山峰</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>本周三（3月26日），纽约著名的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/karen-o-michael-stipe-kim-gordon-flea-to-perform-at-patti-smith-tribute-show-3818559">卡内基音乐厅将主持“人民拥有力量：庆祝帕蒂·史密斯（Patti Smith）致敬音乐会”</a> ，其中包括全明星阵容，由音乐家向传奇的帕蒂·史密斯（Patti Smith）致敬。</p><p>以前宣布的表演的人包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/karen-o">Karen O</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-stipe">Michael Stipe，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kim-gordon">Kim Gordon</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/flea">Flea</a>等。表演者的阵容将由由史密斯乐队的长期成员托尼·沙纳汉（Tony Shanahan）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/flea">跳蚤</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队</a>巡回鼓手史蒂夫·乔丹（Steve Jordan）领导的家庭乐队的支持。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDIdO_5ILm-/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,